{"tid":1477753,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"七月份本港清樓指數","createTime":"2019-08-16T08:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T06:51:05.000Z","uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"65833bd584a413f42376f76020a4efbf5444c15e","tid":1477753,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:33:56.000Z","msg":"青樓指數：<br />\n<br />\n本港七月份新來港初入行青樓女子佔整體68%<br />\n<br />\n比上月新增28%<br />\n<br />\n嫖客七月人均消費大跌37%，平均每位嫖客七月份消費386港圓<br />\n<br />\n數據反映大量內地求職者因經濟環境變差轉職至本港青樓業，但業績未達預期。受本港政局影響，嫖客指數大降，本港七月份嫖客人均叫雞少於一次。業界極度關注其趨勢影響行業正常運作。"},{"pid":"f8c9bcf51f0ab074547f6cf3cf7b5bbdd9df2bb4","tid":1477753,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7136670dea4b67ab03742f08a389c2a39942e9","tid":1477753,"uid":33292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T09:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8780bea97c72764d158a8c76de4e0befc035cd26","tid":1477753,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:51:05.000Z","msg":"👍🏻"}]}